project_descr: The objectives of the project is to 1) identify Yemen’s contributions to the post-2020 global climate agreement known as (INDC) and to 2) strengthen Yemen’s preparation for UNFCCC COP21 negotiations on INDCs leading to the post-2020 agreement

outputs.output_descr: Yemen’s National Preparation for Post-2020 Contributions

project_title: yemen’s national preparation for post-2020 contributions
